query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q1 s t1 tq1 u1) NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('dba',
'drupal',
'es',
'gis',
'ru')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('enterprise-geodatabase',
'print-composer',
'веб-программирование')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Civic Duty',
'Cleanup',
'Curious',
'Enthusiast',
'Explainer',
'Famous Question',
'Necromancer',
'Organizer',
'Quorum',
'Self-Learner',
'Strunk & White',
'Vox Populi') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
